				(property "Description" "Wio-WM1110 LGA-80 module: Semtech LR1110 (LoRa + GNSS + Wi-Fi scan) + Nordic nRF52840 (BLE/Thread/Zigbee). Datasheet V1.3, authored against Table 1 pinout. I2C/UART/SPI are not dedicated pins — assigned via the nRF GPIO matrix; this design uses Nordic SDK defaults (I2C0 SDA=P0.26 pin18, SCL=P0.27 pin16; UART TX=P0.06 pin32, RX=P0.08 pin33)."
